 Reference Number: 220 2506 MHU Job Description: 
To develop and implement effective organisational development and human resources management strategy and action plans which drive the organisation-wide planned change, accountability-based culture, design components, people management programmes and processes required to support the broader business unit strategy and taking cognisance of corporate HR strategic objectives and programs. This role plays a business strategic partner role to the MD and management teams, an employee sponsor or advocate and a change facilitator. Responsibilities: Requirements: Qualification and Skill Benefits and Contractual information: